{"tid":1893063,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"填海華竟然寫歌為醫護人員打氣","createTime":"2020-02-23T03:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T05:35:49.000Z","uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffa52d5f2ccfcfb4083727db125bba8d1e88ff74","tid":1893063,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T03:52:09.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係唱普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都係好難聽<br />\n<br />\n唱粵曲一樣<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n華仔憑歌寄意主唱、填詞一曲《我知道》為醫護人員「疫」境中打氣 💪🏻<br />\n<br />\n因為一張網上圖片上的語句：「我不知道你是誰 但我知道你為了誰￼￼」觸動了華仔寫了這首歌詞，向「疫」境中的￼醫護人員致敬和感謝🙏<br />\n#劉德華<br />\n#華仔天地￼￼<br />\n#醫護人員<br />\n#同心抗疫<br />\n<br />\n#我知道<br />\n歌詞～<br />\n￼￼<br />\n從不 哼半聲 的做 你的胸襟比天空更高<br />\n明知 痛苦的風暴 為你天光天黑禱告<br />\n人生 OH忐 忑路 就算小心免不了跌倒<br />\n難關 更顯得驕傲 那種光輝應該找到<br />\n<br />\n共我不是同生 你怎麼可做到<br />\n漆黑中的眼睛 等待清早<br />\n一雙手已疲累你至今未停步<br />\n濃濃情義我已知道 都知道<br />\n<br />\n沒有計劃 來世 再可天荒地老<br />\n這刻中的結識 盼望得到<br />\n只想需要明日你過得比我好<br />\n同年同月今生今世 同老<br />\n//"},{"pid":"c17fae3568cdd3df1665a7afe8e0bc0c0cbc6283","tid":1893063,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"藍醫護表示多謝華仔"},{"pid":"0046262d2311088b6f9540cd71c87b8a327353b1","tid":1893063,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:00:56.000Z","msg":"冇人想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89752c8165c326ee8a5ed1002a4fbb13330034e7","tid":1893063,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T04:19:42.000Z","msg":"填海華 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f61d4c0ce543566221095c33ec96f9ca9eb0e1","tid":1893063,"uid":35422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T05:35:49.000Z","msg":"填海華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}